      <h2 class="display">Bid blind. The scale lights up when you're close.</h2>
      <p class="lead">Each side sets the number they can live with. Neither sees the other's. The scale stays dark while you're far apart — and only glows once your figures land within 10% of the amount in dispute. Cross over, and it's a deal.</p>
